content: Curious: Does anyone know if Camp Kamala trainings are happening this cycle? I attended in 2020 and loved it and would love to do it again. I know there are some in person ones in CA.

I've seen a few people post some for this cycle, yes. I would check your state channel (and state on events.democrats.org) for that since it seems to fall under more regional and local jurisdiction, not national. ðŸ™‚
